{"tid":612470,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"洛賓同列貝利真係j死人","createTime":"2018-04-01T00:28:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T12:12:35.000Z","uid":141225,"like":211,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"43f55aa2feca0cf4d4650be86032dd125b86f21c","tid":612470,"uid":141225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T00:28:59.000Z","msg":"記得列貝利岩岩踢拜仁個陣 大戰不萊梅嘅迪亞高 已經覺得點解會有人好波到咁 啲技術細膩 加埋佢唔樣靚仔 完美咁將右腳cup大位個潮流帶入市場<br />\n<br />\n洛賓的軌跡唔洗講 佢隻左腳嘅球感 世界上一定係頭三 全世界都知佢下下得隻左腳 都mark唔住佢 即使佢得cup大位同蕩角兩招大技 直到而加都仍然可以咁勁<br />\n<br />\n最特別嘅就係列貝利同洛賓有時會走埋一邊一齊踢 <br />\n變咗雙翼踢埋一邊 攻擊力加乘<br />\nRobbery依個組合真係見過最賞心悅目同大殺傷力嘅雙翼齊飛<br />\n<br />\n見到佢哋慢慢老去 下季佢哋好可能拆夥 好唔捨得<br />\n陪伴住我成長嘅robbery呀~"},{"pid":"89f4fb28587ce39107196b89e04e5a58fb8da503","tid":612470,"uid":30081,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T00:39:13.000Z","msg":"列貝利 絕對係一線頭"},{"pid":"bda3914ed11d11265eb9eb05130cfc6ed2d69cbf","tid":612470,"uid":50770,"like":103,"dislike":7,"score":96,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T00:39:17.000Z","msg":"列貝利係右腳打左中場既潮流帶入市場？有冇問過皮里斯？"},{"pid":"cb34daeeaa53d330ee2f04e327963fc2b4d7bf63","tid":612470,"uid":30081,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T00:42:40.000Z","msg":"利雲度夫斯基 又係j死人"},{"pid":"166d06ff05827ef28a9e6b292cb43b7872644100","tid":612470,"uid":90767,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T00:49:12.000Z","msg":"洛賓 荷蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df56afe7950ba2cf6ca3e52c87d376709d2c5517","tid":612470,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":31,"score":-31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T00:49:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cced719f7239472292b1fdb1e3b7a2ba8062a9c0","tid":612470,"uid":85819,"like":5,"dislike":33,"score":-28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T00:51:05